						<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">________________________________</span></span></span></p><p><br></p><p><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">Bewerbung als Einreise- beamter </span></span></span></p><p><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">D</span></span></span><span style="color:rgb(255,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">L</span></span></span><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">R</span></span></span><span style="color:rgb(255,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;">P</span></span></span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><strong><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:'Comic Sans MS';"><span style="font-size: 22pt;">T</span></span></span></strong><strong><span style="color:rgb(0,0,255);"><span style="font-family:'Comic Sans MS';"><span style="font-size: 22pt;">e</span></span></span></strong><strong><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:'Comic Sans MS';"><span style="font-size: 22pt;">a</span></span></span></strong><strong><span style="color:rgb(0,0,255);"><span style="font-family:'Comic Sans MS';"><span style="font-size: 22pt;">m</span></span></span></strong><strong><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:'Comic Sans MS';"><span style="font-size: 22pt;"> B</span></span></span></strong><strong><span style="color:rgb(0,0,255);"><span style="font-family:'Comic Sans MS';"><span style="font-size: 22pt;">e</span></span></span></strong><strong><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:'Comic Sans MS';"><span style="font-size: 22pt;">w</span></span></span></strong><strong><span style="color:rgb(0,0,255);"><span style="font-family:'Comic Sans MS';"><span style="font-size: 22pt;">e</span></span></span></strong><strong><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:'Comic Sans MS';"><span style="font-size: 22pt;">r</span></span></span></strong><strong><span style="color:rgb(0,0,255);"><span style="font-family:'Comic Sans MS';"><span style="font-size: 22pt;">b</span></span></span></strong><strong><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:'Comic Sans MS';"><span style="font-size: 22pt;">u</span></span></span></strong><strong><span style="color:rgb(0,0,255);"><span style="font-family:'Comic Sans MS';"><span style="font-size: 22pt;">n</span></span></span></strong><strong><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:'Comic Sans MS';"><span style="font-size: 22pt;">g</span></span></span></strong></p><p><strong><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:'Comic Sans MS';"><span style="font-size: 22pt;">________________________________</span></span></span></strong></p><p><br></p><p><strong><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 18pt;">OOC- Informationen</span></span></span></strong></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><strong><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 18pt;">Name: </span></span></span></strong><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 18pt;">Luka Demian Tekeste</span></span></span></p><p><strong><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 18pt;">Alter  : </span></span></span></strong><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 18pt;">15</span></span></span></p><p><strong><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 18pt;">geb am: </span></span></span></strong><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 18pt;">20.10.2006</span></span></span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><strong><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 18pt;">Über mich <img src="https://forum.dlrp.eu/images/smilies/emojione/263a.png" alt=":)" title="smile" class="smiley" srcset="https://forum.dlrp.eu/images/smilies/emojione/263a@2x.png 2x" height="23" width="23" loading="eager"></span></span></span></strong></p><p><br></p><p><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 15pt;">Hallo Server- Team. Ich heiße Luka Tekeste, komme aus der Stadt Baden Baden. Ich fahre gerne Fahrrad in meiner Freizeit, spiele gerne Computerspiele und erforsche die Natur. Geduld,Interesse, Diskrieminierung und Aufmerksamkeit sind meine Fähigkeiten.</span></span></span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><strong><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 21pt;">IC- Informationen </span></span></span></strong></p><p><br></p><p><strong><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 21pt;">_____________________                           ____</span></span></span></strong><img src="https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/Y-ene6magqCNR3Y3_2JkK8zgcak37Lq6-TYWQXwhhnt3dVtRO3kzM5ZwGBXv81XbKiYmgXO6NM0ORhLPTtdv0V2fWt1BdF9EZ-Hxx4jfB7mY-lVTbpEkdheLQ4oORp1hnl7qgre3cLtJ1o_iBA" width="204" height="254" alt="Y-ene6magqCNR3Y3_2JkK8zgcak37Lq6-TYWQXwhhnt3dVtRO3kzM5ZwGBXv81XbKiYmgXO6NM0ORhLPTtdv0V2fWt1BdF9EZ-Hxx4jfB7mY-lVTbpEkdheLQ4oORp1hnl7qgre3cLtJ1o_iBA" class="jsResizeImage"></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><strong><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 18pt;">Name: </span></span></span></strong><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 15pt;">M</span></span></span><span style="color:rgb(111,168,220);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 15pt;">a</span></span></span><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 15pt;">n</span></span></span><span style="color:rgb(74,134,232);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 15pt;">f</span></span></span><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 15pt;">re</span></span></span><span style="color:rgb(74,134,232);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 15pt;">d</span></span></span><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 15pt;"> H</span></span></span><span style="color:rgb(74,134,232);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 15pt;">a</span></span></span><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 15pt;">n</span></span></span><span style="color:rgb(74,134,232);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 15pt;">f</span></span></span></p><p><strong><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 18pt;">Alter</span></span></span></strong><strong><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 15pt;">  :  </span></span></span></strong><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 15pt;">21</span></span></span></p><p><strong><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 18pt;">geb am : </span></span></span></strong><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 15pt;">20.10..2000</span></span></span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><strong><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 18pt;">Über mich   <img src="https://forum.dlrp.eu/images/smilies/emojione/263a.png" alt=":)" title="smile" class="smiley" srcset="https://forum.dlrp.eu/images/smilies/emojione/263a@2x.png 2x" height="23" width="23" loading="eager"></span></span></span></strong></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 15pt;">Sehr geehrtes Server-Team, mein Name ist Manfred Hanf, ich komme ursprünglich aus Der Stadt Hamburg und bin jetzt seit einer Weile in der Stadt hier angereist. Meine Hobbys sind Essen gehen, Auto fahren und Orte besuchen. Meine Famillie wohnt in Pakistan, da komme ich ursprünglich her. Ab zu zu telefonieren wir ein bisschen. Ich habe mich als Einreisebeamter beworben da ich Interesse an dem Job habe. Ich bin allergisch gegen Pollen. Meine Stärken sind Kritik annehmen, geduldig sein, gut zuhören und Loyalität. Mich würde es sehr freuen wenn sie mich annehmen würden. </span></span></span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><strong><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 18pt;">Warum ich und kein anderer?</span></span></span></strong></p><p><br></p><p><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 15pt;">Nun, ich zeige selber sehr Interesse an dieser Arbeit, und wertschätze es zu 100 % bei eurem Team dazuzugehören…</span></span></span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><strong><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 18pt;">Meine Ziele bei euch im Server- Team </span></span></span></strong></p><p><br></p><p><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 15pt;">Meine Ziele in eurem Team ist Vertrauen zu gewinnen, Moderator zu werden und cool mit jedem von euch zu sein. </span></span></span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><strong><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 18pt;">Erfahrungen als Supporter</span></span></span></strong></p><p><br></p><p><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 15pt;">Ich habe relativ viel Erfahrung als Supporter, Moderator, da ich auf vielen Servern im Team war, z.b Gambo World, 4 Blocks</span></span></span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><strong><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 18pt;">Erfahrungen generell im RP</span></span></span></strong></p><p><br></p><p><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 15pt;">Ich spiele fast seit einem Jahr RP, und mir macht es unheimlich Spaß. Ob Polizist, Medic, Admin oder normaler Zivilist, Das RP- Leben ist vielseitig und da wird einem nie langweilig.</span></span></span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><strong><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 18pt;">Schlusswort </span></span></span></strong></p><p><br></p><p><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 16pt;">Mich würde es unheimlich freuen wenn ich angenommen werde. Da ich selber super gerne auf dem Server spiele.</span></span></span></p><p><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 16pt;">Mein Traum ist es schon seit einem Jahr Teil eines Teams zu sein wo der Server gut ist, und viele drauf spielen. Mich würde es glücklich machen wenn ihr mir das ermöglicht.</span></span></span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 15pt;">Respektvoll   </span></span></span></p><p><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 15pt;">Erfahrung im Umgang mit Waffen</span></span></span></p><p><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 15pt;">Sportlich</span></span></span></p><p><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 15pt;">Teamfähig</span></span></span></p><p><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 15pt;">Kritikfähig</span></span></span></p><p><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 15pt;">Loyalität</span></span></span></p><p><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 15pt;">Aufmerksam</span></span></span></p><p><br></p><p><strong><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 18pt;">Schwächen </span></span></span></strong></p><p><br></p><p><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 15pt;">Alleine sein </span></span></span></p><p><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 15pt;">Dunkelkeit </span></span></span></p><p><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 15pt;">nervös </span></span></span></p><p><br></p><p><strong><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 18pt;">Woran ich arbeite! <img src="https://forum.dlrp.eu/images/smilies/emojione/263a.png" alt=":)" title="smile" class="smiley" srcset="https://forum.dlrp.eu/images/smilies/emojione/263a@2x.png 2x" height="23" width="23" loading="eager"></span></span></span></strong></p><p><br></p><p><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 15pt;">Respektvoller werden in manchen Situationen <img src="https://forum.dlrp.eu/images/smilies/emojione/1f914.png" alt=":/" title="unsure" class="smiley" srcset="https://forum.dlrp.eu/images/smilies/emojione/1f914@2x.png 2x" height="23" width="23" loading="eager"></span></span></span></p><p><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 15pt;">Ernst bleiben in manchen Situationen </span></span></span></p><p><br></p><p><strong><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 15pt;"> </span></span></span></strong></p><p><strong><u><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 15pt;">ONLINE-ZEITEN</span></span></span></u></strong><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 15pt;">: Sehr Oft in nächster Zeit </span></span></span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><strong><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 18pt;">Hier erreicht ihr mich…</span></span></span></strong></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><strong><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 15pt;">Email: </span></span></span></strong><a href="mailto:lukatekeste123@gmail.com"><u><span style="color:rgb(17,85,204);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 15pt;">lukatekeste123@gmail.com</span></span></span></u></a></p><p><strong><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 15pt;">DC    :  </span></span></span></strong><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 15pt;">rechteckluka#0750</span></span></span></p><p><strong><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 15pt;">Steam: </span></span></span></strong><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 15pt;">ManfredHanf</span></span></span></p><p><br></p><p><strong><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 17pt;">Mit liebe entworfen    </span></span></span></strong><strong><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Pacifico, cursive;"><span style="font-size: 30pt;">Luka aka Manfred</span></span></span></strong></p>]]></content:encoded>
